node.text:
Had a blast running around LA’s Melrose Ave for Vogue’s Shopping Challenge! Animal prints for any occasion! 🐾 
#vogueshoppingchallenge 

This episode of The Shopping Challenge was filmed pre-pandemic and before social distancing guidelines were issued.

@vogueparis @vogueitalia @voguechina @britishvogue @voguespain @voguejapan @voguerussia @voguetaiwan @voguegermany @vogueindia @voguemexico

node.text:
Let's get fit!  Check out my workout session with @Shawn_Booth18, of BOOTHCAMP, followed by a Happy Hour Q&A. 
Support BOOTHCAMP instructors and staff via tips through Venmo @boothcampgym or paypal.me/boothcampgym. @MichelobULTRA and their partner @OptimumNutrition are matching funds raised up to $7,500.

Grab your mat, chill your beer, and get ready to MOVE.SWEAT.BEER. #MOVEMENTbyMichelobUltra

node.title: MOVEMENT by Michelob ULTRA Home Workout
